<HEAD>
<TITLE>Planning Circle Financial Group Inc.: Our Mission</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="images/pcfgbkgd.jpg">

<CENTER>
<TABLE>
<TR>
<TD><IMG SRC="images/pcfg.gif"></TD>
<TD><H1>PLANNING CIRCLE<br>FINANCIAL GROUP Inc.</H1></TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
</CENTER>

<HR>

<B>Planning Circle Financial Group</B> is an independent financial planning company, providing individuals and companies with complete financial services.
<P>
Under the direction of a team of fully accredited Chartered Financial Planners with more than 30 years of combined experience in the financial and investment fields, <B>Planning Circle Financial Group</B> is optimally equipped to offer its clients a variety of financial planning strategies and investment vehicles.
<P>

<H1>What we do</H1>
As an independent financial planning company, <B>Planning Circle Financial Group</B> presents an independent viewpoint and thus is able to create a personal financial plan for each client.  We provide our clients with expert tax, investment, retirement, and estate-planning services.
<P>

<H1>Our 4 step approach</H1>
<UL>
<LI>Define your current financial position through a personal financial review and analysis.
<LI>Identify both your short term and long term financial goals.
<LI>Implement a financial plan that will achieve your stated goals.
<LI>Review and update your financial plan regularly.
</UL>
<P>

<H1>We Offer</H1>
RRSP's, Guaranteed Investment Certificates, Registered Retirement Income Funds, Life Income Funds, Mutual Funds, Group RRSP's, Annuities, Life Insurance and Disability Insurance.
<P>
As an independent financial planning company <B>Planning Circle Financial Group</B> is pleased to represent such industry leaders as: Trimark, Templeton, Mackenzie, Fidelity, Dynamic, Canadian International, A.G.F. and 20/20.
<P>
