<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>Trimark Fund</H1>

<P>

Introduced in September 1981, the objective of Trimark
Fund is to achieve significant capital growth with a high degree
of reliability in the long run. Capital is invested in leading
international companies whose technology, inventiveness or entrepreneurship
gives them a competitive advantage in the marketplace. 
<BR>
<I>Eligibility:</I> Eligible for the foreign-content portion of registered plans.
<BR>
<I>Fund number:</I> CDN$ 251, US$ 351. 
<P>
<HR>

<CENTER>
| <A HREF="#portfolio">Investment Portfolio</A> | <A HREF="#historical">Historical Compounded Total Rates of Return</A> |<BR>
| <A HREF="#performance">Investment Performance</A> | <A HREF="#summary">Summary of Portfolio</A> | <A HREF="#distributions">Distributions</A> |
</CENTER>

