<HEAD>

<TITLE>Planning Circle Financial Group: Trimark Select Canadian Growth Fund</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="images/pcfgbkgd.jpg">

<A HREF="../pcfg/"><IMG SRC="images/pcfgsm.gif" ALT="Return to the Planning Circle Financial Group Home Page" WIDTH=75 HEIGHT=71 BORDER=0 ALIGN=RIGHT></A>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>Trimark Select Canadian Growth Fund</H1>
<P>

<HR>

<P>
Modelled after Trimark Canadian Fund and Trimark RSP Equity Fund, Trimark <I>Select</I> Canadian
Growth Fund was introduced in November 1992.  Its objective is to achieve significant capital growth
over the long term with a high degree of reliability.  <B>Eligibility:</B> Fully eligible for registered plans.  
<B>Fund Number:</B> 158/258.
<P>


