<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>Trimark <I>Time</I><B>Piece</B>.</H1>
<H2 ALIGN=CENTER><I>Reflecting the proven investment philosophy behind Trimark Mutual Funds</I></H2>
<P>

Trimark <I>Time</I><B>Piece</B> is an interactive software program for your Windows PC or Mac computer.
<P>
It will show you how time-based investment strategies and timely advice from a qualified financial adviser
to develop a personal financial plan... and follow it through.  It shows how inflation and delay work against
you.  And how sound financial planning, regular investing and investment performance can work for you.
<P>
Best of all, Trimark <I>Time</I><B>Piece</B> is complimentary.  All you have to do is complete this form and your software will be mailed to you.
<P>
Trimark is one of Canada's largest mutual fund investment managers.  Our patient, bottom-up investment approach, long-term performance and high quality service have helped us achieve and maintain consistent growth in assets.
<P>
Trimark <I>Time</I><B>Piece</B> puts the power of that thinking at your fingertips.  Send for your complimentary disk now... then talk to your financial adviser about the best way to get the proven investment
strategies working for you.
