<HEAD>

<TITLE>The Evening News: 03/25/96</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<H1>
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="../../../images/evening.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"><BR>
On-Line Archive
<H2>Monday, March 25, 1996 <IMG SRC="../../../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
</H2>

</CENTER>
</H1>

<UL>
<LI>OPSEU - OFL Demo 
<LI>By-elections 
<LI>Quebec By-elections 
<LI>Mad Cow Update 
<LI>Oscar Advancer 
</UL>

<HR>

<H3>OPSEU - OFL Demo</H3>

<P>
At least 2-thousand members of the Ontario labor movement gathered
at Queens Park today to protest last Monday's tactics by the OPP
riot squad. The group is also demanding the resignation of Solicitor
General Bob Runciman. 
<HR>

<H3>By-elections </H3>

<P>
Canadians in six federal riding have their say today. Two by-elections
are being held in Newfoundland, three in Quebec and one here in
Ontario in the riding of Etobicoke. For the Liberals, the votes
are a test of their national unity strategy. 
<HR>

<H3>Quebec By-elections </H3>

<P>
In the Quebec races, the Bloc Quebecois is expected to hold onto
one. 
<P>
The others have been held by Liberals for decades. and top candidates
have been parachuted in making the challenge a little tougher
for all involved. 
<HR>

<H3>Mad Cow Update </H3>

<P>
Britain's government has decided against new action to protect
the public from &quot;mad cow disease&quot;. 
<P>
There are fears that the disease can lead to a fatal brain ailment
in humans, and about 20 countries have banned imports of British
beef. 
<P>
Today the European union joined the ban. For years, Canada has
banned beef imports from Britain and any other country that has
a problem with mad cow disease. 
<HR>

<H3>Oscar Advancer </H3>

<P>
Excitement, and crowds, are building in tinseltown for the Oscars
tonight. 
<P>
Mel Gibson's movie &quot;Braveheart&quot; leads the way with 10
nominations including one for best picture. Fans have been camped
out at the Dorothy Chandler Pavilion since Friday, in hopes of
catching a glimpse of their favorite star. 
 <P>
<CENTER><IMG WIDTH=585 HEIGHT=30 SRC="../../../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>

