<HEAD>

<TITLE>We welcome your contributions to "Community File".</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">

<CENTER><IMG WIDTH=524 HEIGHT=85 SRC="../../images/commfile.gif" ALT="Community File Logo" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>

<P>
Extending our community spirit, CHCH presents <I>Community File</I>, highlighting local
events and entertainment. 
<P>
<I>Community File</I> is seen three times each weekday on CHCH-TV: between 9:00am-10:00am, 2:00pm-3:00pm, and 4:00pm-5:00pm. 
<P>
We invite your input on <I>Community File</I>. Please mail the
details of your community event, three weeks in advance, to:
<PRE>
          Community File
          CHCH-TV
          P.O. Box 2230, Station A
          Hamilton, Ontario
          L8N 3A6
</PRE>

<P>
We also accept e-mail submissions. Send them to: <A HREF="mailto:commfile@chch.wic.ca">commfile@chch.wic.ca</A>.
<P>
Please note: Although we try to include as many community and
local events as possible, due to the great number of submissions
for <I>Community File</I>, we cannot guarantee your event will
be featured.  Submissions are selected based on a &quot;first come, first served&quot; basis.
<P>
<A HREF="../../news/communityfile/">Return to this week's <I>Community File</I>.</A>
<P>

