<HEAD>
<TITLE>CHCH Operations: Master Control</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">
<HR>
<CENTER><H1>On-Air Operations: Master Control</H1></CENTER>
<HR>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../gifs/newcen3.gif"></CENTER>

<HR>

<P>Master Control is the broadcast centre of CHCH-TV.  It is here
that  programs are integrated with commercials and formated into a
complete  broadcast schedule.

<P>Master Control is built around  an audio/video switcher which allows
for  smooth transitions between an array of video sources, both inside
the  station, across the region via microwave, and around the world via 
satellite.  A computerized system of integrating commercial and program
playbacks is linked to a Sony LMS (Library Management System) (pictured
above), which executes seamless playbacks from four self-contained
videotape machines... offering instant access to over 1000 audio/video
elements.

<BR>
<HR>
<h3><UL>
<LI><A HREF="opervtr.htm">Videotape</A></LI>
</UL></h3>
<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>
<CENTER><TABLE COLSPACE=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="operprod.htm"><IMG SRC="../images/leftarro.gif" border=0 ALT="Left Arrow Icon"><BR><B>Production Services</B></A></TD>
<TD><IMG SRC="../images/blank.gif"></TD>
