<HEAD>
<TITLE>CHCH Operations: Videotape</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">
<HR>
<CENTER><H1>On-Air Operations: Videotape</H1></CENTER><HR>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../gifs/oneinch.gif"></CENTER><HR>

<P>Our videotape facilities (VTR) offer a full complement of
professional  television formats from Betacam SP, to 1" and 2" formats. 
There are  more than a dozen machines, providing the full range of
professional  broadcast playback systems. As well, VTR provides access
to satellite feeds for recording, dubbing, closed captioning and program
playback.
<h3>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="opermc.htm">Master Control</A></LI>
</UL>
</h3>
<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>
<CENTER><TABLE COLSPACE=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0>
