<HEAD>

<TITLE>Studio 'A'</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
 <HR>

<H1><CENTER>Studio &quot;A&quot;</CENTER></H1>
<HR>

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../gifs/studio5.gif"></CENTER> 
<P>
<I>On the set of &quot;Boogie's Diner,&quot; in CHCH-TV's Studio
&quot;A.&quot;</I><HR>

<P>
<B>The largest of CHCH studios, Studio &quot;A&quot;s 4000 square
feet has served as the home of numerous sitcoms, telethons, specials
and events.</B><HR>

<P>
THE STUDIO
<UL>
<LI>Studio size 50' X 80 ' (4000 square feet)
<LI>Cyc height -- 20' 6&quot;
<LI>Height to ceiling -- 22ft.
<LI>Removable drop grid for lighting
<LI>Located on main floor, near loading docks
<LI>Heavy duty heat pumps for studio cooling
<LI>Serviced by mobile ( see <A HREF="supercr.htm">Supercruiser</A>
or <A HREF="ultracr.htm">Ultracruiser</A>)
</UL>
<HR>

<P>
PRODUCTION FACILITIES
<P>
<I>Full Office, Dressing Rooms, Make-Up and Green Rooms Provided</I>
<UL>
<LI>5 separate offices plus a large reception area (1300 square
feet)
<LI>5 separate dressing rooms (479 square feet)
<LI>Green room with kitchenette (14 X 13'5'')
<LI>Large, 3 chair, make-up room with double sink (10'4''X11')
<LI>Separate washroom and shower facilities
<LI>Located near commissary and board room
<LI>Washer &amp; Dryer on site
</UL>
<HR>

<P>
LIGHTING AND POWER
<UL>
<LI>Strand Mantrix 2X control board
<LI>Strand CD80 dim packs
