<TITLE>The CHCH Telecentre</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
 <HR>

<H1><CENTER>CHCH Telecentre</CENTER></H1>
<HR>

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../gifs/studio3.gif"></CENTER> 
<P>
<I>Our Telecentre studio is a versitile facility that can accomodate
small, medium, and large scale productions of all natures.</I>
<HR>

<P>
<B>The CHCH Telecentre has served as the production studio for
numerous CHCH productions as well as national and international
television programming.</B>
<P>
<B>The Telecentre is a well serviced television studio designed
upon the framework of a large movie theatre. On a location separate
from our main studios, it provides excellent flexibility and independence
for production teams, plus high visibility with extremely convenient
access to Toronto.</B><HR>

<P>
STUDIO
<UL>
<LI>Studio size 44' X 66 ( 2904 square feet)
<LI>Grid height -- 13' 6&quot;
<LI>Serviced by mobile ( see <A HREF="supercr.htm">Supercruiser</A>
or <A HREF="ultracr.htm">Ultracruiser</A>)
</UL>
<HR>

<P>
PRODUCTION FACILITIES
<UL>
<LI>2 -- Dressing Rooms with self-contained washroom and shower
facilities
<LI>2 -- Green Rooms
<LI>Make-up room
<LI>Pull-out bleachers in studio
</UL>
<HR>

<P>
LIGHTING AND POWER
<P>
<I>Strand Control board </I>
<UL>
<LI>54 -- 2 kW dimmers
<LI>36 -- 2 kW non-dimmable
<LI>6 -- 5 kW dimmers
<LI>2 -- 5 kW non-dimmable
</UL>

<P>
PLUS
<P>
<I>Strand Mantrix control board</I> 
<UL>
<LI>3 -- CD 80 dim packs 12 -- 2.4 kW dimmers
</UL>

<P>
