<LI>18 -- Zips 1K
<LI>14 -- Zips 2K
<LI>38 -- Par 64
<LI>6 -- Strand Leko
<LI>8 -- Parlipsphere
<LI>18 -- E.T.C.
<LI>32 -- Mizar 200w
<LI>2 -- Soft light kit 4K
<LI>14 -- Stands 2K
<LI>8 -- Stands 1K
<LI>12 -- Grip stands
<LI>12 -- Grip heads
<LI>All lights fully equipped with barndoors, gel frames, grates
and screens
<LI>Flags, sandbags, adapters, A.C. cable, gaffer grips
</UL>
