<TITLE>Studio 'B'</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
<HR>

<H1><CENTER>Studio &quot;B&quot;</CENTER></H1>
<HR>

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../gifs/studio1.gif"></CENTER> <BR>
<I>Studio &quot;B&quot; provides facilities for many varied programs.</I>
<HR>

<P>
<B>Studio &quot;B&quot; offers an economical &quot;true studio&quot;
environment, excellent for the efficient production of panel,
talk and magazine styled programs, as well as commercials and
product shots, and corporate videos.</B><HR>

<P>
STUDIO
<UL>
<LI>Studio size 32' X 28 ' (900 square feet)
<LI>Cyc height -- 11' 6&quot;
