Pre/post direct outputs
<LI>4 sub masters, each with direct output and full aux. capabilities
<LI>Stereo and mono outputs
<LI>2 1/4 &quot; stereo reel to reel tape deck
<LI>ITC mono cart machine with record capability
<LI>1 Sony CDP-790 CD player
<LI>1 Studer A710 cassette deck
<LI>1 Phone coupler
<LI>Digicarts and DAT available on request
<LI>Stereo monitoring capability with Auratone T6 monitor speakers
