<HEAD>

<TITLE>SuperCruiser </TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
<HR>

<H1><CENTER>The CHCH SuperCruiser</CENTER></H1>
<HR>

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../gifs/truck.gif"></CENTER> <HR>

<P>
<B>The CHCH SuperCruiser is a self-contained production unit housed
in a 42 foot tractor trailer and is used for both studio and remote
multi-camera productions. It provides effective facilities for
the production of music, drama, sports, and special event programs.
</B><HR>

<P>
PRODUCTION CONTROL ROOM
<UL>
<LI>Operating console with positions for Technical Director, Director
and Production Assistant.
<LI>Production console with positions for Producer, font co-ordinator
and font operator.
</UL>
<HR>

<P>
MONITOR WALL
<UL>
<LI>2 Ikegami 20&quot; colour monitors - program and preview
<LI>28 -- 9&quot; monochrome monitors - cameras, VTRs, effects
and utility
<LI>2 Panasonic 8&quot; colour monitors - chyron program and preview
<LI>12 -- 5&quot; monochrome monitors - preview switcher effects
</UL>
<HR>

<P>
SWITCHER
<UL>
<LI>GVG 3000-2 Digital Switcher
<LI>32 inputs
<LI>2-M/E
<LI>Dual Component Chroma key
<LI>Disk storage of switcher set-up
</UL>
<HR>

<P>
VIDEO FACILITIES
<UL>
<LI>5 Ikegami 323's with Fuji 44:1 lenses
<LI>2 HL55 hand-helds with Canon 18x lenses
<LI>1 HL55A hand-held with Canon 18x lens
<LI>3 -- 4 field Frame Syncs
<LI>1 RCA LPS camera
<LI>Vinten fluid heads for all hand-held cameras
<LI>2 Sachtler Vario Ped pedestals for hand-held cameras
<LI>3 studio conversion kits with matte boxes &amp; filters for
hand-held cameras
<LI>Golf cart, field dolly, scaffolding and low swivel seat mount
available
<LI>Mobile roof deck reinforced for camera position
<LI>Configured for 10 cameras, ability to interface more
</UL>
<HR>

<P>
DIGITAL EFFECTS : Abekas A51+ featuring:
<UL>
<LI>rotation
<LI>perspective
<LI>expansion
<LI>page turn
<LI>infinite cropping
<LI>superwarp
<LI>multi-picture
<LI>key channel
<LI>skew
<LI>sizing
<LI>posterization/solarization
<LI>A/B switching
<LI>100 event memory
<LI>off-line storage on 3.5&quot; floppy disks
<LI>A53 - Compatable
</UL>
<HR>

<P>
STILL STORE : Leitch Video Dual Channel Still File
<UL>
<LI>Supported by main frame, control panel, status monitor, air
and preview channel monitors
<LI>Video viewed and frozen in frame buffer and recorded into
image storage drive
<LI>Stills may be stored as field, frame or colour frame
<LI>Capacity for 1,500 fields
<LI>Images may be recalled sequentially, randomly, or arranged
into sequence lists
<LI>Features include transition effects, compression, position,
as well as keying and duration of display
<LI>Streamer tape drive compatible with Abekas
</UL>
<HR>

<P>
GRAPHICS <BR>
Infinit with Transform
<UL>
<LI>3 buffers
<LI>32 meg of Ram
<LI>1.2 Gb harddrive
<LI>150 meg Input/Output bernoulli
<LI>support for 90 meg bernoulli<BR>

</UL>

<P>
Chyron 4100 EXB Dual Channel
<UL>
<LI>Hard drive and MGM
<LI>Channel combine module (CCM)
<LI>Two 8&quot; disk drives
<LI>2 Panasonic colour monitors for operator.
</UL>
<HR>

<P>
VIDEO TAPE FACILITIES:
<UL>
<LI>1 Sony 3100 1&quot; Recorder with enhanced TBC for superior
slow motion and freeze frame capability
<LI>2 Sony BVH 2000, type &quot;C&quot;, 1&quot; Recorders with
full slow motion and freeze frame capability
<LI>2 BVW 75 Beta SP Recorders with controllers
<LI>1 Sony BVU 800 3/4&quot; Recorder
<LI>Telecom Research time-code generator with Colour Frame
<LI>Capability of adding additional machines at clients request
<LI>Audio, video routing to all machines
<LI>4 colour monitors for input/output of machines
<LI>8 monochrome monitors for previewing sources
<LI>1 VHS machine
<LI>Burned in timecode for VHS and 3/4&quot; if required
</UL>
<HR>

<P>
INTERCOM<BR>
Ward-Beck 24 x 24 Communications Matrix
<UL>
<LI>6 External drops for A.D.s, lighting, etc.
<LI>6 I.F.B.s all with talkback
<LI>Producer and Director intercom panels are 24 keys each, including
all Externals and I.F.B.s
<LI>Technical Director has a separate 12 key panel
<LI>Separate key panels at the secondary Production Desk for the
font Operator, font Co-ordinator, and Producer
<LI>Capable of being interfaced to most other systems
<LI>7 UHF walkie-talkies with base station, headsets, earpieces
and speaker mics<BR>

</UL>

<P>
Onyx - VS 8-line phone system
<UL>
