<LI>8 sub-master, each with direct outputs and full aux. capabilities
<LI>8 BBS DPR 404 compressor/de-essers
<LI>pre-wired to feed Ampex MM1200 16-track machine
<LI>16-channel mixdown section
<LI>5 auxiliary outputs. Pre/post capable
<LI>stereo and mono outputs
<LI>Monitoring via 2- JBL 4311 or Auratone 5RC
<LI>distribution throughout mobile via routing switcher
<LI>12 spare distribution amplifiers
<LI>48 mic inputs with switch able phantom power
<LI>36 trunk lines
<LI>2 Video monitors - program and switch able preview
<LI>1 Otari 4 track 1/4&quot; stereo reel to reel deck
<LI>2 ITC cart machine with recording capability
<LI>1 Tascam CD601 CD player with remote
<LI>1 Sony cassette deck
<LI>1 Phone coupler
<LI>Digicarts and DAT available at request
<LI>2000 feet multi cable, 2000 feet mic cable and auxiliary equipment
