<HEAD>

<TITLE>The CHCH UltraCruiser</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
 <HR>

<H1><CENTER>The CHCH UltraCruiser</CENTER></H1>
<HR>

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../gifs/ultra.gif"></CENTER> <HR>

<P>
<B>The CHCH UltraCruiser is a self-contained production unit housed
in a 45 foot tractor trailer and is used for both studio and remote
multi-camera productions. It is suitable for the production of
drama, sitcom, and live event programming.</B><HR>

<P>
PRODUCTION AREA
