<TITLE>CHCH NewsLink Microwave Vehicles</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
 <HR>

<H1><CENTER>CHCH &quot;NewsLink&quot; Microwave Vehicles</CENTER>
</H1>
<HR>

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../gifs/van.gif"> <IMG SRC="../gifs/vanint.gif"></CENTER>

<P>
<I>CHCH boasts the operation of two NewsLink Microwave Vehicles.</I>
<HR>

<P>
<B>Microwave trucks have a variety of capabilities for inventive
producers ranging from live event coverage, to commercial and
promotional event coverage, and teleconferencing. Our microwave
vehicles are based on Ford 350 Econoline van chassis with the
capacity for multi-camera switching, recording and editing, in
addition to stereo audio capabilities. These microwave vehicles
are equipped with 2.5ghz and 7ghz microwave transmitters, with
a range of approximately 40 to 50 miles.</B><HR>

<P>
<CENTER>For further information, contact: Jim McDougall, Dominic
Stanchieri or Wilf Venne, (905) 522-1101,
<P>
Toronto Direct Line 366-9688, Fax: (905)527-5022/(905) 645-3217
or
