<HEAD>

<TITLE>Andrew Robertson Biography</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
 <HR>

<H1><CENTER>Andrew Robertson</CENTER></H1>
<HR>

<P>
He asked me to write a &quot;bio&quot; for our web site.
<P>
&quot;On who?&quot; I asked.
<P>
&quot;On you&quot; He replied.
<P>
&quot;On me?... OK&quot; I said, &quot;but I refuse to write in
the third person, it's like writing an obituary.&quot;
<P>
&quot;Just do it the way you want&quot; was the reply, &quot;and
don't be afraid to toot your horn!&quot;
<P>
&quot;Cool&quot; I thought, &quot;Stay tuned for horn tooting&quot;
<P>
I've been involved in the commercial production industry ever
since 1986. That's when I emerged from Humber College's three
year film and television production program. I was ready to take
on the world, unfortunately, I was also dirt poor and desperate
for a job. The Partners Film Company gave me that first break.
After working there for almost three years, having gone from truck
driver to assistant editor, I came to the conclusion that I had
to do my own thing.
<P>
That flash of self analytical insight brought me to the CBC Windsor.
Management felt I could revitalize their commercials and on-air
look. However, events conspired against us... budget cutbacks
deemed the entire Windsor operation redundant and we were all
out of work just three months later. C'est la vie at the CBC.
<P>
What was CBC's loss was CHCH's gain. I started here in 1991, and
immediately became the catalyst that landed some of the most exciting
and important commercial accounts to date. Since then I've continued
to write, direct and produce a wide variety of projects ranging
from commercials to on air promotions and corporate videos. Along
the way I've amassed an extensive collection of awards and gained
a reputation as one of Hamilton's leading television advertising
creative forces. So, If you're talking commercial production in
Hamilton, you're talking to me... sooner or later, preferably
sooner. <HR>

<P>
<CENTER>For further information, contact: Jim McDougall, (905)
522-1101, ext. 251,
<P>
Toronto Direct Line 366-9688, Fax: (905) 645-3217 or
<P>
E-mail your questions or comments to
<A HREF="mailto:production@chch.wic.ca">production@chch.wic.ca</A></CENTER>
<HR>

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>
<CENTER><TABLE COLSPACE=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="operprod.htm"><IMG SRC="../images/leftarro.gif" border=0 ALT="Left Arrow Icon"><BR><B>Production Services</B></A></TD>
<TD><IMG SRC="../images/blank.gif"></TD>
<TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="/"><IMG SRC="../images/home.gif" border=0 ALT="Home Page Icon"><BR><B>CHCH Home Page</B></A></TD>
