<HEAD>

<TITLE>The New World Wine Tour: Show Profile</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="../images/winelogo.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
<IMG SRC="../images/barred.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
</CENTER>

<P>
<I><B>The New World Wine Tour</B></I> is a new, half-hour &quot;infotainment&quot; program featuring intelligent editorial on the Canadian wine industry.  This finely crafted and highly entertaining, consumer-focused program concentrates on the unique and beautiful areas, rich in history, culture, and heritage of our Canadian industry, which is gaining both domestic and international recognition.
<P>
The current season focuses on Canadian wine from the Niagara region with sub-themes including the growing process, tourist attractions, recreation, history, heritage and hospitality.  The series is shot entirely on location in the Niagara penninsula, with the overall tone being casual, candid, informative and entertaining.
<P>
<I><B>The New World Wine Tour</I></B> explores the cultural context of wine and its marriage to cuisine coming to us from one of the world's youngest and most prominent wine regions.
<P>
Hosted by Jonathan Welsh, of &quot;E.N.G.&quot; and &quot;Adderly&quot; fame, celebrity guests are welcomed along with featured chefs from Niagara's participating hotels and restaurants.  A Canadian viticulturalist or wine maker joins the dining experience to provide authoritative insight.
<P>
This season, celebrity guests have included: Red Green, Pierre Burton and Dinah Christie.
<P>
<I><B>The New World Wine Tour</B></I> continues to provide valuable information
to novice and expert wine enthusiasts <U>Sunday afternoons at 5:00 p.m.</U> <B>CHCH-TV</B>. 

<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="../images/barred.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
<BR>
| <A HREF="../winetour.htm">Return To <I>The New World Wine Tour</I> Home Page</A> |<BR>
| Send your comments to <A HREF="mailto:winetour@chch.wic.ca">winetour@chch.wic.ca</A>
|
<BR>
<IMG SRC="../images/barred.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
