<HEAD>

<TITLE>Jonathan Welsh Biography</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<P>

<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="jwelsh.jpg">
<H1><I><B>Jonathan Welsh</B></I>
<BR>
<I><B>Host/Co-Producer</B></I></H1></CENTER>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/barred.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>

<P>
A popular and well-liked performer, Jonathan Welsh is an award winning actor on such internationally acclaimed series as &quot;Adderly&quot; and &quot;E.N.G.&quot;.  Additionally, Mr. Welsh is also known throughout the country for his dedication to the off-camera advancement of literacy through his national charity, <I>Performers For Literacy</I>.
<P>
His career spans stage and screen from the musical &quot;Hair&quot; to the exciting &quot;New World Wine Tour&quot;.
<P>
A published poet and committed Canadian, he is a firm believer in the role of the Arts in a vibrant Canada for the next century.

