<HEAD>

<TITLE>Forevergreen Television & Film Productions Inc.</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<P>

<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="../images/barred.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
<H1>Forevergreen Television &amp; Film Productions Inc.</H1>
<IMG SRC="../images/barred.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>
<P>

<H3><B>A Unique Approach</B></H3>

<I>Forevergreen</I> designs practical marketing solutions that effectively counter the many problems that arise from the increasingly fragmented marketplace.
<P>
<I>Forevergreen</I> embraces traditional and non-traditional marketing options to create new and exciting methods for reaching target-specific demographics with valuable spillover into secondary markets.
<P>
The non-traditional approach <I>Forevergreen</I> incorporates is based on sound marketing techniques.  Each project is designed to deliver a well-balanced, imaginative campaign that implements six guiding principles:
<UL>
<LI>Creative Solutions
<LI>Responsible Budgeting
<LI>Technical Excellence
<LI>Project Substance
<LI>Sustained Market Presence
<LI>Measurable Results
</UL>

<P>

<H3><B>Our &quot;Positive Impact&quot; Mandate</B></H3>

&quot;Do something good for your product and service, by doing something good for people.&quot;
<P>
<I>Forevergreen</I> recognizes the challenge of selling to an increasingly &quot;aware&quot; consumer base.  This includes the selling of product, service, image or ideas.
<P>
<I>Forevergreen</I> is compelled by a mandate that is lean, green and clean.  Dedicated to social-issue marketing, <I>Forevergreen</I> excels in providing clients with value-added opportunities that present their products and services in a refreshing and responsible manner.
<P>
<I>Forevergreen</I> is a fully-bilingual company and maintains a formal association with a wide variety of specialized suppliers.  Suppliers that provide distinctive talents and skills which are required for specific challenges.  Every aspect of every campaign is managed by the best possible professionals.  Consistency is maintained under the direction of <I>Forevergreen</I>'s three partners, who design and oversee each project while maintaining ongoing client rapport.
<P>
This approach yields continually refreshing creative, maximum technical expertise, and sound financial management.
<P>
<I>Forevergreen</I> believes in the win, win, win scenario:
<B>The Client wins, the Consumer wins, and Society wins.</B>

<I>Forevergreen</I> is an <A HREF="awards.htm">award-winning</A> company.


<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/barred.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
<H3>
Forevergreen Television &amp; Film Productions Inc.<BR>
181 Carlaw Avenue,<BR>
Suite 230,<BR>
Toronto, Ontario<BR>
M4M 2S1<P>

Telephone: (416) 778-9944<BR>
Fax: (416) 778-9951</H3>
