<TITLE>CHBC-TV, Kelowna, B.C.</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/chbc.gif"> </CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER>342 Leon Avenue, Kelowna, British Columbia, V1Y 6J2</CENTER><BR>
<CENTER>Tel.: (604) 762-4535  Fax: (604) 868-0662</CENTER>

<HR>
<P>
Nestled in the heart of British Columbia, &quot;The Okanagan's Very Own CHBC&quot; 
coverage area stretches from the U.S. border to Revelstoke in the Rockies.  The region's
key urban centres include Kelowna, Vernon and Penticton.
<P>
CHBC is dedicated to a local perspective.  It is effective because the <I>CHBC News at 5:00</I>
has consistently delivered a share of over 50%.  CHBC's locally scheduled programming
outperforms the network by 3 to 1.  The commercial production department is one of the most award
winning in Canada.  Companies are flocking to the Corporate Video Division to have first rate
videos produced at very competitive prices.
<P>
The success of CHBC is built on the talents of motivated people committed to excellence in local 
television service.  The vision which sets us apart from the competition is that we are truly the
Okanagan's very own TV station.
