<HEAD>

<TITLE>CHCH, Hamilton, Ontario</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/chch.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER>163 Jackson Street West, Hamilton, Ontario, L8N 3A6</CENTER><BR>
<CENTER>Tel.: (905) 522-1101, Fax: (905) 523-8011</CENTER>

<HR>

<P>
CHCH-TV, Canada's first english-language independent television station, has been entertaining and 
informing viewers for over 40 years.  With an audience exceeding 4.2 million people in Southern Ontario, the 
station can also be seen coast-to-coast in non-metropolitan areas via Canadian Satelite Communications Inc. 
(Cancom).
<P>
CHCH-TV provides a broad range of quality entertainment, news and sports programming.  When it comes to 
news programming, CHCH-TV dominates its regional market - Hamilton, Halton and Niagara.  CHCH-TV is a leader in mobile production, boasting a growing demand for its crews and facilities from third party business.  The station is also a dynamic, imaginative marketing partner, consistently developing effective campaigns for its 
advertisers.  As well, the station is actively involved in its community, lending support to the area's many 
non-profit organizations and local events.

