<HEAD>

<TITLE>CICT TV, Calgary, Alta.</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/cict.gif"></CENTER>
<H1><CENTER>CICT - Calgary, Alta.</CENTER></H1>

<P>
<CENTER>222 - 23rd St. N.E., Calgary, Alberta, T2E 7N2</CENTER><BR>
<CENTER>Tel.: (403) 235-7777  Fax: (403) 248-0252</CENTER><HR>

<P>
Over forty years ago, in 1954, television was a completely new concept and CHCT-TV, as it was then known,
was the very first television station in Calgary.  In October 1957, CHCT became an affiliate of the Canadian Broadcasting 
Corporation.  On September 1, 1975, CHCT disaffiliated from the CBC to become Calgary's only local independent station,
a position held ever since.
<P>
As a WIC independent, <B>Calgary 7</B> has both the national strength and local flexibility to cater to viewers needs.  A greater 
freedom and creativity with programming and the ability to develop innovative plans for station image, news, sales, 
promotion and community projects is exercised.
<P>
Viewers tuning in to <B>Calgary 7</B> see the top-rated shows of today, along with a full line-up of local productions including 
live news, sports, information and entertainment programming.  During hockey season, <B>Calgary 7</B> broadcasts a full schedule
of Calgary Flames home games.
<P>
<B>Calgary 7</B> operates from a large scale, state of the art facility and boasts an internationally honoured, award-winning
creative team.  The <B>Calgary 7</B> News Department employs the latest technology with satellite and ENG microwave 
vehicles, allowing us to cover breaking stories live, as they happen.
<P>
Long recognized as <I>the</I> local television station, <B>Calgary 7</B> plays an integral role in the community and is proud
of the relationship with its viewers and the citizens of Calgary.  <B>Calgary 7</B> lends its support to a wide variety of community
projects both large and small.
<P>
Through its on-going partnership with the community, <B>Calgary 7</B> has also developed strategic alliances with many advertisers
and clients.  <B>Calgary 7</B> leads the way in creating imaginative and effective sales promotions that deliver the clients
message and promote <B>Calgary 7</B> programming.
<P>
<B>Calgary 7</B> is dedicated to providing the best entertainment and information programming to attract and serve it audience.








