<HEAD>

<TITLE>RDTV, Red Deer, Alta.</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/rdtv.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER>2840 Bremner Avenue, Red Deer, Alberta, T4R 1M9</CENTER><BR>
<CENTER>Tel.: (403) 346-2573  Fax: (403) 346-9980</CENTER><HR>

<P>
RDTV serves Central Alberta from the Rockies to Saskatchewan and, by cable, into Calgary and 
Edmonton.  In the last four years, RDTV has come from RDTV? to RDTV!  With a great cast of innovative
players, the station has swept CanPro for the last two years consecutively and has garnered other national
and international awards.
<P>
RDTV's production staff is constantly in demand from movie videos to bi-weekly satellite cattle auctions,
from award-winning commercials to rodeos.  RDTV's <I>Makin' 8</I> series of on-location shoots at rodeos 
has given the sport a new lease on life.  The series is in its third year and is now being courted internationally. 
RDTV's children's programming claims a large viewing audience throughout the province and an off-shoot
of that was the formation of the <I>Toon Crew Club</I> in 1994.  At 30,000 strong, its members are a force to
be reckoned with!



