<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">
<P>
 
<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/moviem.gif"></CENTER>

<P>
<B>MovieMax!</B> offers movies of the 60s, 70s, and 80s to viewers in
Western Canada. From blockbusters to cult classics and everything in between.
All unedited and commercial-free in an eighteen hour day format. 
<P>
