decades, but it also provides these films in special thematic blocks.  There are evenings
dedicated to westerns, comedies, dramas, plus many others.  Also, subscribers enjoy
the special &quot;<B>MovieMax!</B> Salutes,&quot; which recognizes notable stars and directors
featured in the month's programming
