<HEAD>

<TITLE>Western Broadcast Sales</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
 
<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/wbs.gif"></CENTER>


<P>
With offices in Toronto, Montreal, Vancouver and Winnipeg, Western
Broadcast Sales is Canada's largest national television sales
organization. In addition to its marketing and sales efforts on
behalf of all eight Westcom TV Group stations to national advertisers,
WBS also represents another 16 television stations throughout
Canada. Its in-depth coverage of the Canadian television marketplace
allows WBS to provide national advertisers with superior service
and a unique ability to respond directly to their communications
needs with a variety of custom solutions.
<P>
In addition to capturing improved shares of traditional national
television advertising revenues for its client stations, WBS has
developed several &quot;emerging business&quot; development units
designed to promote the use of television and create new revenues
for the medium of the national and regional levels.

