Vancouver's leading radio station is <B>CKNW/98</B>.  Unmmatched in information programming and <I>the</I> major
news source in BC, <B>CKNW</B> is recognized for breaking stories before all others.  <B>CKNW</B>'s excellence
in information programming is achieved through the efforts of the best and largest group of radio news, sports, and 
commentators in Canada.  Listeners are accustomed to hearing the voices of the country's most respected broadcast
journalists. And BC's most listened to radio station offers an interactive exchange of opinions and ideas with its audience.
<P>
