Western Canada's largest radion audience turns to the NW Sports Network for live play-by-play broadcasts of all
Vancouver Canucks, BC Lions, and Vancouver Grizzlies games.
<P>
<B>CKNW/98</B> sponsors an astonishing number of showcase and charity events each year, and as a result, 
is the most visible media team in Vancouver.
