<HEAD>
<TITLE>QR77 Calgary, Alta.</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../images/bkgd.jpg">

<P>
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="../images/qr77.gif" ALT="QR77 Logo" WIDTH=225 HEIGHT=105 BORDER=0>
</CENTER>

<CENTER>
<H1>QR77, Calgary, Alta.</H1>
</CENTER>

<HR>

<P>
<B>QR77</B> is Calgary Information Radio, a news, talk and information
station broadcasting a powerful 50,000 watts day and night on
770 AM (Khz) and 88.9 cable FM (Mhz).
<P>
<B>QR77</B> is Calgary's source for news, sports, information, advice
and entertainment.  
<P>
<B>QR77</B> provides listeners with comprehensive round-the-clock news coverage,
up-to-date weather, traffic reports from Calgary's only traffic
plane, dynamic sports coverage and reports, compelling talk shows
and advice on relationships, home improvement, gardening, computers,
health, money, plus more!
<P>
<B>QR77</B> is also very involved in the Calgary community either directly
or indirectly with a number of groups and organizations that do
community work in the city. 
<P>
<B>QR77</B>'s programming appeals to a broad and diverse 25+ audience in
Calgary, Central and Southern Alberta and beyond.
<P>

