<HEAD>
<TITLE>"Touched by an Angel", premieres January 5, 1997 on CHCH-TV.</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/release1.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE"></CENTER>
<H2 ALIGN=RIGHT><I><B>December 24, 1996</B></I></H2> 

<CENTER>
<H1>&quot;Touched by an Angel&quot;</H1>
<H2>premieres January 5, 1997 on CHCH-TV.</H2>
</CENTER>


<P>
<I><B>Touched By An Angel</B></I>, the inspiring drama about angels
who help mortals through confused and troubled times, premieres
<U>Sunday, January 5, 1997 (8:00 - 9:00 p.m.)</U>, on <B>CHCH-TV</B>,
simulcast/<B>CBS</B>.<BR>

<P>
The popular series, which debuted in the fall of 1994, stars <B>Della
Reese, Roma Downey</B> and <B>John Dye</B>.<BR>

<P>
<I><B>Touched By An Angel</B></I> is about a supervising angel
(Reese) and a junior angel (Downey) who, together, offer hope
and direction to individuals temporarily sidetracked for reasons
as varied as there are people.  In the end, faith does endure
and a seemingly merciless world softens to the gentle nudge of
one of heaven's own. <BR>

<P>
<I><B>Touched By An Angel</B></I> premieres <U>Sunday, January
5, 1997, at 8:00 p.m.</U> on <B>CHCH-TV,</B> simulcast/<B>CBS</B>.
<BR>
<BR>
<P>

