<HEAD>

<TITLE>"Dot and Spot's Magical Christmas Adventure" a holiday special on CHCH-TV.</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/release1.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE"></CENTER>
<H2 ALIGN=RIGHT><I><B>December 3, 1996</B></I></H2> 

<CENTER>
<H2>CHCH-TV has the delightful holiday special</H2>
<H1>&quot;Dot and Spot's Magical Christmas Adventure&quot;</H1>
</CENTER>

<P>
Dot and Spot , a couple of lovable Dalmatian puppies, rescue Santa
Claus on Christmas Eve with the help of two youngsters, who learn
to appreciate the magic of Santa and their new home.  <I><B>Dot
and Spot's Magical Christmas Adventure</B></I> airs <U>Thursday,
December 19, 1996 (8:00 - 8:30 p.m.)</U>, on <B>CHCH-TV</B>.<BR>

<P>
In <I><B>Dot and Spot's Magical Christmas Adventure</B></I>, the
Marshall family has just moved from New York City to the wilds
of Colorado, a transition that has proven difficult for the two
Marshall children, Ryan and Robin, but particularly for Ryan,
who thinks that Colorado is  the scariest place he has ever known.
 The only thing not frightening to Ryan are his father's two rescue
puppies -- Dot and Spot, who are determined to show the little
fellow that his new home is not all that bad.<BR>

<P>
Then, on Christmas Eve, the adventure begins.  When Dot and Spot
use the telescope on the Marshall's Observation Deck to search
for Santa's sleigh, they find that the jolly old soul is in trouble.
 Immediately they run to wake up Ryan to lead him to the Observation
Deck, and in their excitement, also wake up Robin.  Next, the
foursome make their way through the treacherous snow, wind and
rocky terrain to free Santa and his reindeer from the boulders
that hold them captive.  <BR>

<P>
During the rescue mission, the children hear Dot speak.  It is
at that point that Dot and Santa explain that &quot;on Christmas
Eve, it just takes very special ears and an open heart to hear
all living things communicate.&quot;  Ryan then realizes how much
one can see and hear when not afraid and gains a new appreciation
for the natural beauty that surrounds his new home.  <BR>

<P>
<I><B>Dot and Spot's Magical Christmas Adventure</B></I> airs
<U>Thursday, December 19, 1996, at </U>
<P>
<U>8:00 p.m.</U> on <B>CHCH-TV</B>.<BR>

<P>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>
<CENTER>
<TABLE COLSPACE=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="../press.htm"><IMG SRC="../../images/leftarro.gif" border=0 ALT="Left Arrow Icon"><BR><B>For Immediate Release</B></A></TD>
<TD><IMG SRC="../../images/blank.gif"></TD>
