<HEAD>

<TITLE>"Countdown To Grey Cup '96" on CHCH-TV.</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/release1.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE"></CENTER>
<H2 ALIGN=RIGHT><I><B>November 13, 1996</B></I></H2> 

<CENTER>
<H1>&quot;Countdown to Grey Cup '96&quot;</H1>
<H2>on CHCH-TV</H2>
</CENTER>


<P>
Originating live from downtown Hamilton, the hub of this year's
Grey Cup celebrations, <I><B>Countdown to Grey Cup '96</B></I>
will examine the state of Canada's national sport, provide an
in-depth look at both competing teams and offer up-to-the minute
predictions, as everyone revels in all the festive fun of Grey
Cup madness!  <I><B>Countdown to Grey Cup '96 </B></I>airs <U>Saturday,
November 23, 1996, (5:00 - 5:30 p.m.)</U> on <B>CHCH-TV</B>.<BR>

<P>
Hosting the half-hour news production special will be CHCH's own
sports team: <B>Fred Anderton, Paul Hendrick, Steve Ruddick </B>and<B>
Ken Welch.<BR>
</B>
<P>
The first quarter of <I><B>Countdown to Grey Cup '96 </B></I>will
include lively interviews with the CFL Commissioner, Larry Smith,
the man caught in the crossfire with Player Association President
Dan Ferone.<BR>

<P>
Live from the designated party tent and the city's streets, the
second quarter will assess the two teams matched up for the great
kick-off.  The Eastern Division will be covered by Fred Anderton
and Steve Ruddick will look at the West Division team.<BR>

<P>
The third quarter will recap the various social activities that
have taken place over the  week leading up to the big event, while
the fourth quarter will focus on up-to-the-minute expectations
and all the unbridled excitement connected with the country's
biggest sports party.<BR>

<P>
Share in the unmistakable spirit of Grey Cup -- watch <I><B>Countdown
to Grey Cup '96</B></I> <U>Saturday, November 23, 1996 at 5:00
p.m.</U> on <B>CHCH-TV</B>.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>

<P>


