<P>
Brian Linehan is back on television and doing what he does best
-- interviewing the most fascinating and compelling people in
the world of entertainment.  <I><B>Linehan</B></I>, with his new
weekly half-hour series premiering in January, 1997, will launch
with a one hour special on <U>Saturday, November 16, 1996 (7:00
- 8:00 p.m.)</U>, on <B>CHCH-TV</B>.<BR>

