Brian Linehan's special will include revealing interviews with
such legendary personalities as <B>Barbra Streisand, Arnold Schwarzenegger,
Anthony Hopkins, Bugs Bunny</B> and more, plus feature the latest
in show biz news.<BR>

<P>
Brian Linehan, an entertainment journalist who's interviewing
skills are legendary, returns to television after an eight year
hiatus to host, <I><B>Linehan</B></I>, a one hour special airing
<U>Saturday, November 16, 1996, at 7:00 p.m.</U> on <B>CHCH-TV</B>.
