<HEAD>

<TITLE>"Canadians On-Line", a documentary special on CHCH-TV.</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../images/bkgd.jpg">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/release1.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE"></CENTER>
<H2 ALIGN=RIGHT><I><B>August 26, 1996</B></I></H2> 

<CENTER>
<H1>&quot;Canadians On-Line&quot;</H1>
<H2>A Documentary Special</H2>
<H2>on CHCH-TV.</H2>
</CENTER>

<P>
<I><B>Canadians On-Line</B></I>, a timely call to action and examination
of what some pioneering individuals, businesses and entire communities
are doing to prepare for 'tomorrow' and the emerging information
age, airs <U>Saturday, September 14, 1996 (9:00 - 10:00 p.m.)</U>
on <B>CHCH-TV</B>.<BR>

<P>
Like the traditional literacy skills asked of the industrial worker,
the next generation of jobs and economic opportunities will demand
fluency and comfort with computer and communications tools as
well as the culture that embraces them.  With that in mind, <I><B>Canadians
On-Line</B></I> will offer job seekers, workers, parents, youth,
seniors, minorities, business people and, basically, anyone concerned
about their future, a revealing look at people like themselves
who are changing their lives.<BR>

<P>
What does 'being digital'  in the computer communications revolution
really offer up to the average person today and what should we
all be preparing for, for tomorrow?  Through the actions and words
of dozens of Canadians -- from St. John's to Vancouver -- living,
learning and working interactively and on-line, <I><B>Canadians
On-Line</B></I> endeavours to find the answer.<BR>

<P>
<I><B>Canadians On-Line</B></I>, a Forevergreen Production, airs
<U>Saturday, September 14, 1996 at 9:00 p.m.</U> on <B>CHCH-TV</B>.

<P>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>
<CENTER>
<TABLE COLSPACE=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="../press.htm"><IMG SRC="../../images/leftarro.gif" border=0 ALT="Left Arrow Icon"><BR><B>For Immediate Release</B></A></TD>
<TD><IMG SRC="../../images/blank.gif"></TD>
<TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="/"><IMG SRC="../../images/home.gif" border=0 ALT="Home Page Icon"><BR><B>CHCH Home Page</B></A></TD>
<TD><IMG SRC="../../images/blank.gif"></TD>
<TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="mailto:programming@chch.wic.ca"><IMG SRC="../../images/mail.gif" border=0 ALT="Mail Icon"><BR><B>programming@chch.wic.ca</B></A></TH></TD>
</TABLE></CENTER>
<CENTER>
