<HEAD>

<TITLE>Danielle Steel's "Full Circle", on CHCH-TV</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY background="../../gifs/bkgd.jpg">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/release1.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE"></CENTER>
<H2 ALIGN=RIGHT><I><B>August 14, 1996</B></I></H2> 

<CENTER>
<H1>&quot;Full Circle&quot;</H1>
<H2>Danielle Steel's Gripping Drama</H2>
<H3>on CHCH-TV</H3>
</CENTER>

<P>
A woman, traumatized by rape at a young age, gradually learns
to trust and love again as she finds success and happiness as
a lawyer, wife and mother in <I><B>Danielle Steel's Full Circle</B></I>,
airing <U>Sunday, September 8, 1996 (9:00 - 11:00 p.m.)</U>, on
<B>CHCH-TV</B>.<BR>

<P>
<B>Teri Polo</B> (TV Credits: <I>Northern Exposure,
People Like Us</I>; Film Credits: <I>House of the Spirits, Born
To Ride</I>), <B>Corbin Bernsen</B> (TV Credits: <I>L.A. Law,
Love Can Be Murder, Grass Roots, Beyond Suspicion, I Know My Son
is Alive</I>; Feature Film Credits: <I>Major League, Major League
2, S.O.B., Hello Again</I>), <B>Eric Lutes</B> (<I>Caroline in
the City</I>), <B>Reed Diamond</B> (<I>Homicide: Life on the Street,
Awake to Danger, Her Hidden Truth</I>) and Emmy Award winner <B>Erika
Slezak</B> (<I>One Life to Live</I>) star. <BR>

<P>
In <I><B>Danielle Steel's Full Circle</B></I>, Tana Roberts (Polo)
is determined not to end up like her mother (Slezak) -- a cheerless
individual involved with a married man.  However, fate may force
her to fall into the same emotional traps.

<P>
When Tana is raped by the son of her mother's lover, she turns
to her studies to help mask the painful experience.  She also
shies away from men, except for one college friend, Harry Winslow
(Diamond).   During the time he is hospitalized, Tana meets his
father, Harrison (Bernsen), a recent widower.  The two find comfort
in one another and fall in love.  However, out of her respect
for Harry, Tana terminates the liaison .<BR>

<P>
After a time, Tana is confronted with another dilemma as she becomes
attracted to a handsome attorney (Lutes) still entangled with
his estranged wife.  <BR>

<P>
If Tana is to elude her mother's mistakes, she must finally face
her past and trust that she will one day find true love.  <I><B>Danielle
Steel's Full Circle</B></I> airs <U>Sunday, September 8, 1996,
at 9:00 p.m.</U> on <B>CHCH-TV</B>, pre-release/NBC.<BR>

<P>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/bar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></CENTER>
<CENTER>
